==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Extendible
<hw>Ex*tend"i*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Capable of being extended, susceptible of being stretched,
extended, enlarged, widened, or expanded.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>Liable to be taken by a writ of
extent.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Extendlessness</ent>⟦br⟧
